1. What can you do to prime your audience for awesome ideation?
Solution : B. Start with creative warm-up exercises that get people to think outside the box and have fun

2. How can you inspire your audience to stretch their imagination?
Solution : A. Share inspirational stories of innovations relevant to your organization and customers

3. How do Job Stories help your team succeed?
Solution : D. They help you embody your customer and understand their situation, motivations, and goals, which will then help inspire new products or services
